{"tid":397134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[火攻] 網購蠟燭滅曱甴惹火　劏房險付之一炬","createTime":"2017-09-12T08:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T11:49:46.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0ecb3ad9e01959ded0c3377b76e19ed4bd16c1","tid":397134,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:48:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>網購蠟燭滅曱甴惹火　劏房險付之一炬</strong><br />\n<br />\n荃灣發生蠟燭焚宅火警。中午12時11分，大河道57號卓明大廈樓上一個劏房單位，突然閉門失火，鄰房住客及時發現，立即報警，消防破門入屋，開動一條喉迅速將火救熄，僅一批雜物焚毀，經調查後，懷疑有人點着蠟燭後離家引致燒着雜物起火。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，起火劏房住有一對夫妻及兩名兒子，其中兄長早前透過網購，由內地購買了專門對付曱甴的蠟燭回家使用，事發前，兄長趁家中各人全部外出後，遂點燃蠟燭。現場消息稱，火警後，有家人抱怨為何要使用該批蠟燭，導致家園起火。"},{"pid":"2fa020411e354c75b10172775c688603d24031b7","tid":397134,"uid":81863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f357376f7884a95dea00eb32a250517a3e16b03","tid":397134,"uid":52068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:51:14.000Z","msg":"曱甴真係害人不淺"},{"pid":"984097c6ca8484a5d15192bf29a361954d4249ca","tid":397134,"uid":23631,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:54:35.000Z","msg":"D蠟燭真係發揮到功效滅左成屋曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5c5bd81410dfb4e11c2b356e900db9cee21db0","tid":397134,"uid":25656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:55:48.000Z","msg":"臨訓見到床有小強係咩玩法。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/396356?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/396356?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c50c62d44c461d09b6ff16eec331e239833ce332","tid":397134,"uid":71676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D蠟燭真係發揮到功效滅左成屋曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高質<img src=